title: Coming back to League after 4 years, can I have some tips on what I need to know and what's changed?
body:
I'm coming back after 4 years simply because this game is still blowing up after 10 years of it being alive. I played back in season 4 and the early realise of the "New Summoners Rift", is there any major changed to characters and what are the new characters like?
